{"tid":273902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消防書色色der？學妹驚叫「學長快射　我受不了」","createTime":"2017-06-07T02:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T04:11:34.000Z","uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e22a6ccfea8e828c860ed8e93248aa3db2575b69","tid":273902,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T02:24:56.000Z","msg":"這實在是很令人不想歪...最近line瘋傳幾頁消防書翻拍內容，其中對話如下&nbsp;「學長，你趕快射，我快受不了了」、「不能太早射，學妹，妳再忍一下，找到點之後就會射了」、「好，學妹，找到了握緊！」；「學長，為什麼去的時候，你都會射上面？」、「學妹，因為射上面比安全呀！」、「學長，那進去的時候呢？」、「學妹，進去的時候還是會射呀，其實只要進去，都很危險&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於這幾段「學長v.s.學妹」的對話實在有A，因此很多人好奇，這是A書還是消防書，對此，有網友又拍下幾張截圖，「這是正港消防書喔」、「除了射不射之外，下面有寫『火場射水』，務必接近或是找到火點才能射水，勿因感受熱度就盲目射水&hellip;』這是專業文喔」、「消防書這樣寫，也太狂了！」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170605/1133357/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170605%2F1133357%2F&d=s5EF9dUvn4yAA5qclk7%2B4UbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=cd5ee8b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170605/1133357/</a>"},{"pid":"c8db935e2560afca5ff808b64e1c97144f0857e7","tid":273902,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cab33eff286e06777c79ca9bb427ec957022d81","tid":273902,"uid":112198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:04:34.000Z","msg":"台灣 又加一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a876188f35fa6956202c6567a8221986f34fcbde","tid":273902,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"台灣消防書驚現淫邪情節<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/272815/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/272815/page/1</a>"}]}